# Diagrams with Mermaid

Always use Mermaid syntax for diagrams in documentation and responses.

## Supported Diagram Types

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    A[Flowchart] --> B[Sequence]
    B --> C[Class]
    C --> D[State]
    D --> E[ER]
```

## Examples

### Component Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    User --> Component
    Component --> Store
    Store --> API
```

### Sequence Diagram

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    User->>UI: Click button
    UI->>Store: Dispatch action
    Store->>API: Fetch data
    API-->>Store: Response
    Store-->>UI: Update state
```

### State Machine

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Idle
    Idle --> Loading: fetch
    Loading --> Success: resolve
    Loading --> Error: reject
    Success --> [*]
    Error --> Idle: retry
```
